, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/iezypqouqxma8qsaxrah 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/lwpbba2v3iayzmgetosw 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/wdp4c2tf7yzrzc2u2ooz 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/nkcgetxngzn4dyqbjs8y 920w"></figure><p>那么所描述的评分机制就相当于每天看棋盘上的有限块，如果有全黑的行就给他 1 美元；第二天，您扩展该块，收回前一天的所有奖励并重复练习。本质上，我们用序列<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bigvee_{x\le n}\bigwedge_{y\le n}P(x,y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋁</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">≤</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-munderover MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋀</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; 